[{"name":"theme_info","theme_name":"Cortado","theme_author":"22 Agence Créative","theme_version":"1.3","theme_documentation_url":"https:\/\/22agencecreative.ca","theme_support_email":"info@22agencecreative.ca"},{"name":"Readme","settings":[{"type":"header","content":"Welcome to Cortado"},{"type":"paragraph","content":"Cortado is a simple lightweight theme designed for coffee shops or restaurants that sell products online. With the simple and versatile sections, you can create a website that reflects your image and define your online presence."},{"type":"paragraph","content":"This theme is also built for search engine optimisation (SEO) and supports Google Rich Search with the schema.org guidelines for a better indexation of your website, content and products on search engines."},{"type":"paragraph","content":"Let's start creating!"},{"type":"header","content":"Section schema"},{"type":"paragraph","content":"Cortado has several sections which all have multiple settings. For each section, you have access to « general settings » like padding, border-radius, section type, etc. These settings will determine the layout of the section."},{"type":"paragraph","content":"You will then have the « section settings » which are section specific settings like text color, size and content position."},{"type":"header","content":"Theme settings"},{"type":"paragraph","content":"Cortado also has a couple of snippets which all have multiple settings. You'll be able to customize your buttons, product cards, etc. in the sidebar settings, which will be applied all over the store."},{"type":"paragraph","content":"Finally, you have the general settings for the theme. These include section animations settings, general color, typography and font sizes, etc. Those will be in the sidebar settings as well."},{"type":"header","content":"Support"},{"type":"paragraph","content":"If you have any questions, any difficulties or any comments about Cortado, feel free to visit our website and contact us, 